  etherape-0.9.3.ebuild:
  Do not dodoc COPYING/INSTALL, misc fixes, 0.9.3 x86 stable.

*etherape-0.9.3 (19 Aug 2005)

  19 Aug 2005; Marcelo Goes <vanquirius@gentoo.org>
  +files/etherape-0.9.3-res_mkquery.patch, -etherape-0.9.1.ebuild,
  +etherape-0.9.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. Ported res_mkquery.patch to 0.9.3. Compiles and runs with gcc4
  without patching.

  16 May 2005; Aaron Walker <ka0ttic@gentoo.org>
  +files/etherape-0.9.1-gcc4.diff, etherape-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Added patch so etherape will build w/gcc-4.

  10 May 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org> etherape-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  09 May 2005; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> etherape-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

